# Paths the cheap EXECUTOR may never touch (globs, fnmatch-style).
# The executor is a cheap model - keep it away from secrets, infra, and the
# guard system itself. Add your project's sensitive paths here.

# secrets + env
*.env
.env
.env.*
**/secrets/*
**/*secret*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
config/system.env

# the guard system (a cheap model must not weaken its own leash)
guards/*
bin/*
.protected

# CI / infra / deploy
.github/*
**/Dockerfile
**/fly.toml
**/*.tf
**/deploy/*
